name: R4_ucum_common_for_R4B
title: Cross-version VS for R4.Common UCUM units for use in FHIR R4B
description: This cross-version ValueSet represents concepts from http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/ucum-common|4.0.1 for use in FHIR R4B. Concepts not present here have direct `equivalent` mappings crossing all versions from R4 to R4B.
